CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 16, 1945, pg. 18, reads: "The Winner!  - At a recent baby contest sponsored by Carter Chapel AME Church, Patricia Ann Garner was winner of the first prize, a baby doll with ten-dollar bills pinned on it.  Second prize of $5 went to Catherine Strong, and third prize of $2.50 wen to Clyde Reed Jr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Patricia Ann Garner, winner of baby contest sponsored by Carter Chapel AME Church posed with doll covered in dollar bills, Harris Studio, another version
